Dominique Besnehard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dominique_Besnehard 0 Dominique Besnehard (French: [dɔminik bɛsneaʁ]; born 5 February 1954) is a French actor, film producer, casting director, writer and talent manager. He has appeared in over 80 films and television shows since 1975. He starred in the 1983 film À nos amours, which was entered into the 34th Berlin International Film Festival.
